## Women Safety Web Application

This project is a beginner-level web application focused on women safety.
It is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to demonstrate basic frontend
development skills and practical problem-solving.

### Project Objective
The aim of this project is to create a simple and user-friendly interface
that can help in improving awareness and accessibility related to women safety.

### Features
- Simple and clean user interface
- Emergency alert / safety-related information (basic level)
- Interactive elements using JavaScript
- Responsive design for better usability

### Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

### Learning Outcomes
- Improved understanding of frontend web development
- Hands-on practice with JavaScript interactions
- Experience in structuring a real-world themed project

### Future Improvements
- Add real-time location support
- Integrate emergency contact features
- Improve UI and accessibility

### Status
This project is currently under development and will be enhanced
with additional features over time.
